- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new model for software applications that can be used in healthcare organizations.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is another possible category as the paper discusses the potential benefits of using online health forums to improve healthcare outcomes.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new machine learning model for health stage prediction.
